⍝ Compress.tc
⍝ ═══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO Boolean scalar or vector; B nonscalar
      ⍝ inv: ¯1↓⍴Z ←→ ¯1↓⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO ← 2∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,5) (,0 1 0 0 0)     ⍝ 5-element Boolean
      Z ← LO/B
      (¯1↓⍴Z) ≡ ¯1↓⍴B
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
